Scott Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Lawrence 0 Scott Lawrence (born September 27, 1963) is an American actor best known for his role as United States Naval JAG lawyer Cmdr. Sturgis Turner on the CBS series JAG. Lawrence played the role from 2001 until 2005, when the series ended.
